  characterName: Koigakubo Tarou
  description: His struggle to speak makes him a really quiet boy. Most of his responses
    come in the form of a shake or a nod, and any word that leaves his mouth is barely
    audible. He even has a hard time talking to his own mother. Even though his grades
    are alright, his lack of sociability leaves more to be desired. That's why he
    chose to join the student council in hopes of becoming more proactive. His days
    there wouldn't be easy, but through all his troubles, he'd start to grow closer
    to Takano Saki, his classmate who would join the council alongside him.
